{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ebdc8390dc","title":"第二章 上海“文革”时期的婚姻管理","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f63fa7c60c","index":0,"year":2011,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"ebdc8390dc"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3459654dae","name":"限制资产阶级法权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"3766d87da7","name":"革命大批判","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"44f81d89d9","name":"上海辞书出版社","type":"出版方/发行方"},{"id":"5275d10348","name":"破四旧","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"5f6c7e74b5","name":"派性","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","name":"非常与正常：上海“文革”时期的社会生活（上）（上海辞书出版社2011年）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"金大陆著，上海辞书出版社2011年","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"fcdfaa8639","name":"金大陆"}]},"publication_details":{"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ac0187ca4c","type":"paragraph","text":"第二章上海*文革”时期的婚姻管理","index":0,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"40b50d5168","type":"paragraph","text":"一、结婚登记情况分析","index":1,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"4cbc12817d","type":"paragraph","text":"“文化大革命”以前，上海的结婚和离婚登记均由区政府民政科办理。1968年5月，结婚登记下放到各街道办事处。1975-1976年间，各区革命委员会地区组开始接管此事。1977年婚姻登记正式复归民政部门。由此可见，尽管“文革”十年间的婚姻管理模式发生过数次的变动，但基本的管理是持续的和正常的。现根据已出版的上海十区区志的材料，编辑成表：","index":2,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"cd589a0cbb","type":"paragraph","text":"表一1966—1976年上海各区结婚登记情况统计表","index":3,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"ea3df4957f","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：对区名长宁虹口黄浦静安","index":4,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"976341a93e","type":"paragraph","text":"卢湾南市普陀徐汇杨浦闸北总计年份1966","index":5,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"c012dd5f96","type":"paragraph","text":"13242987296022714446","index":6,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"1a351b5233","type":"paragraph","text":"26221667","index":7,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"e9dca392ea","type":"paragraph","text":"31542340237711967222046634558","index":8,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"1e06d893ff","type":"paragraph","text":"3999353538752753","index":9,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"18faae0bc7","type":"paragraph","text":"4743313933485","index":10,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"d47b7f193d","type":"paragraph","text":"20154475447139423305373425231968","index":11,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"9ec51823a3","type":"paragraph","text":"2916279730178184939483887","index":12,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"bfb6f603b7","type":"paragraph","text":"33873298348221791969","index":13,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"5f549bb009","type":"paragraph","text":"4329193628 295","index":14,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"e3eb3a7a63","type":"paragraph","text":"（续表）区名长宁虹口黄浦静安","index":15,"publicationId":"8acb0cd5-669d-450e-98c0-cd24242e480c","articleId":"ebdc8390dc"},{"id":"2e80fbf77b","type":"paragraph","text":